{"tid":1471183,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[和理非全面進場] 連儂牆冇人搞冇人提喇？","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:01:02.000Z","uid":40718,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3187c4790ac3efb9ae189ad6ccd330f05168ef","tid":1471183,"uid":40718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:08:05.000Z","msg":"連儂牆係一個好好嘅文宣同傳播資訊嘅渠道<br />\n之前都有巴打開過post話有中老年人日日去 當報紙咁睇 <br />\n所以大家應該將啲true news 同埋我哋嘅觀點擺上去<br />\n仲要用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大字</span> <br />\n<br />\n唔該和理非同我全面進場 繼續搞好佢<br />\n等多啲人知發生咩事 同埋最緊要係個輿論嘅方向<br />\n哂時間互屌 不如做實事<br />\n<br />\n敵人唔會嫌少 朋友唔會嫌多<br />\n依啲0成本印下嘢痴下牆點解唔做<br />\n拆完就第朝再起 唔使衝突 <br />\n返正每日都有新嘅新聞 有人幫手清理 幾好<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n818見大家"},{"pid":"f5f5b0e17783eaf7e989b48f31b4fd7a94382555","tid":1471183,"uid":40718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:08:23.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"4571b32cbda39f9a62fc6a90ca044674ffbe2c17","tid":1471183,"uid":40718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:08:33.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"dd12d4fe8378edfa63c77edd3d42fc6fd32ed0da","tid":1471183,"uid":40718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:08:45.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"33fb3e9f29b54e332ba1d5f0894081b50497ccd8","tid":1471183,"uid":40718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:09:56.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"f23def4ac0cc714c90c7596362a89e5977f26a3c","tid":1471183,"uid":40718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:10:12.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"1264c341fd0473b44b9531345aa39a5fc4173999","tid":1471183,"uid":40718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:10:43.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"10f380f430f08056accb133a85050014ce00b0dd","tid":1471183,"uid":40718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T